Trade/Device Name(s): On Call Ketone Reagent Strips for Urinalysis
Healthy Me Ketone Reagent Strips for Urinalysis
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for On Call and Healthy Me Ketone Reagent Strips for Urinalysis, qualitative/semi-quantitative detection of ketones in urine for OTC use.
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for over-the-counter qualitative and semi-quantitative detection of ketone (acetoacetic acid) in urine to aid diagnosis of acidosis or ketosis and for monitoring ketogenic diets.
